\begin_inset Formula $j_{a}$
\end_inset

 first and then over 
\begin_inset Formula $i_{a}n_{a+1}$
\end_inset

:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
C_{i_{a+1}j_{a+1}}^{m_{a}n_{a}}=\sum_{i_{a}j_{a}}\sum_{n_{a+1}}C_{i_{a}j_{a}}^{m_{a}n_{a}}M_{i_{a}i_{a+1}}^{*n_{a+1}}M_{j_{a}j_{a+1}}^{n_{a+1}}
