 Of course all the eigen modes are irrelevant except for dominant one so
 the 
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

s cancel and in the end we get 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left\langle \psi|\psi\right\rangle =\lim_{N\rightarrow\infty}e_{max}^{N}
\]

\end_inset

