\begin_inset Formula $L/R$
\end_inset

 partitioned Hamiltonian
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\hat{H}=\hat{H}_{L_{i}}\otimes𝕀_{R_{i}}+𝕀_{L_{i}}\otimes\hat{H}_{R_{i}}+\sum_{ab=1}^{\chi}M_{ab}\hat{h}_{L}^{a}\otimes\hat{h}_{R}^{b}\label{eq:PartitionedHamiltonian}
